UConn Routs Hartford 75-39 in Opening Round of Women’s NCAA Basketball

-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 
2011-03-20T18:37:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-20/uconn-routs-hartford-75-39-in-opening-round-of-women-s-ncaa-basketball.html
The University of  Connecticut 
thrashed the University of Hartford 75-39 in the opening round
of college basketball’s national women’s tournament.  The Huskies are seeking a third straight title in the
National Collegiate Athletic Association tournament. Connecticut
will face No. 8 Kansas State or No. 9 Purdue on March 22.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  